nodes.text: Hi Person1,  I just heard on the news about the spike in COVID cases in LOCATION. I am due to have a cat scan and a bone scan at L&M MM/DD/YYYY and am a little nervous now. Do you think the hospital is safe for me now? My youngest son has MS. He just had an Ocrevus infusion MM/DD/YYYY so we have to be very careful. Thanks Person2
